</target></link><space/>is established</tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell><link><target>Southern African Development Community</target></link><space/>(SADC)</tablecell><tablecell><link><target>South African Rand</target></link><xhtml:br></xhtml:br>(interim proposal)</tablecell><tablecell>Africa</tablecell><tablecell>2016</tablecell><tablecell>To supplement or succeed the<space/><link><target>Common Monetary Area</target><part>CMA</part></link><space/>and<space/><link><target>Southern Africa Customs Union</target></link></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell><link><target>South Asian Association for Regional Cooperation</target></link></tablecell><tablecell></tablecell><tablecell>South Asia</tablecell><tablecell>2016<template><target>Citation needed</target><arg name="date">August 2010</arg></template></tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell><link><target>Union of South American Nations</target></link><space/>(UNASUR)</tablecell><tablecell>Latino<extension extension_name='ref'>Proposed by Ecuador's President Rafael Correa on December 15, 2007</extension></tablecell><tablecell>Latin America<xhtml:br></xhtml:br>/Caribbean</tablecell><tablecell>2019</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell><link><target>Economic Community of Central African States</target></link><space/>(ECCAS)</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell><tablecell>Africa</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell><tablecell>To supplement the<space/><link><target>Economic and Monetary Community of Central Africa</target></link><space/>(CEMAC)</tablecell></tablerow><tablerow><tablecell><link><target>Economic Community of West African States</target></link><space/>(ECOWAS)</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell><tablecell>Africa</tablecell><tablecell></tablecell><tablecell>To succeed<space/><link><target>West African Economic and Monetary Union</target><part>UEMOA</part></link><space/>and<space/><link><target>West African Monetary Zone</target><part>WAMZ</part></lin